<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ف ص م<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣٧٩٢ - ف ص م]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فصَمَ يَفِصم، فَصْمًا، فهو فاصِم، والمفعول مَفْصوم<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• فصَم الشَّيءَ:</span> شقّه، قطعه، صدعه من غير فصل <span class="c1">"فصَم الحِمْلُ ظهره"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• فصَم الورمَ:</span> استأصله.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• فصَم علاقتَه بأخيه:</span> قطعها.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">• فصَم العقدةَ:</span> حلَّها <span class="c1">"فصَم عُرى المودَّة"</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>